Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.43,0:00:15.56,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,This is Kyou, my elder daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.86,0:00:19.66,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,She’s fifteen years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.71,0:00:28.24,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,This one is Asu, my younger daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.67,0:00:30.24,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,She’s only nine years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.29,0:00:38.36,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,To ensure that she doesn’t wake her sister, Kyou\Nalways gets up quickly when the alarm clock rings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.72,0:00:51.53,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Every morning, Kyou leaves to deliver newspapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.00,0:00:57.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’ll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.68,0:00:58.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.99,0:01:06.58,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Asu. I can’t wait for today’s fireworks festival! {festival?}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.10,0:01:16.16,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I’ve always been watching over the two of them from heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.71,0:01:22.95,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I was able to leave behind just one thing for the two of you:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.04,0:01:26.75,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,a small promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.38,0:01:46.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother went to heaven the year she gave birth to Asu. {mel: Our mother went to heaven the year Asu was born.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.57,0:01:49.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our father disappeared after accumulating gambling debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.41,0:01:54.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, we were left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.73,0:01:58.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a 40-year-old, one-room, dilapidated apartment with no bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:00.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is where we live.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.34,0:02:03.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, when spring comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:03:55.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! Onee-chan will be getting home soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:58.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to prepare breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:08.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m finally done.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.51,0:04:14.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, in the past, Asu was the one who really looked forward to the fireworks festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:16.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:22.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Comment: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:24.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:29.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That’s right! The change from yesterday’s grocery shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:40.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m counting on you. I’ve saved up little by little just for this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:45.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan and I are going to have a lot of fun at the food stands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:47.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Candy apples,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:48.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,takoyaki, {melody capitalizes this, wry?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.91,0:04:50.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and rice crackers with sauce.{"senbei" a specific type of Japanese rice crackers, but "doremi just goes with: "Japanese crackers"}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.32,0:04:54.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.18,0:04:56.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:00.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.74,0:05:02.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Breakfast is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.91,0:05:04.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.40,0:05:12.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today's the day of the fireworks festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:14.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:20.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, after I finish cleaning, may I go out for a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.08,0:05:22.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That’s fine. It is Sunday, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:23.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.95,0:05:26.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You’ll find out later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:31.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m going now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.90,0:05:35.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next-door neighbor, your mailbox is full!{yeah, no, it still sounds retarded, but I won’t stand for "neighbor-san", better suggestions desired}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:39.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It’s really full!{don't shout too loudly now, Asu}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:43.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu! Be careful, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:44.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:46.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, seriously, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:48.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You’ll find out later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:53.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Mr. Landlord, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.06,0:05:57.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.36,0:06:15.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!{orig: All right!}{my translation: "hai!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:26.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:33.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn’t Asu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:36.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, it’s Yaoichi’s husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.92,0:06:39.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you going to be selling vegetables at this stand today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.57,0:06:42.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vegetables wouldn’t sell too well at a festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.85,0:06:43.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! These are...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.98,0:06:46.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we’re going to be a candy apple stand today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:49.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really? A candy apple stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.73,0:06:52.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My sister and I will come by later to buy one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:55.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay! Then I’ll prepare an extra large one just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.19,0:06:57.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.61,0:07:05.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There’s the yakisoba stand, the shooting game stand, and the cotton candy stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:14.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It’s done{complete}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.82,0:07:24.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ma’am!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.91,0:07:29.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:33.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.20,0:07:44.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-The money is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.71,0:07:57.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu, I’m home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.82,0:08:00.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry I’m so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:03.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What’s wrong? The lights aren’t even on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.35,0:08:10.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, Asu, it’s a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.71,0:08:12.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A yukata...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:14.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.17,0:08:19.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where’d you get this? {orig: Why do you have this?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:21.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bought it at the Hashimoto clothing store.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:26.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have Mom’s hand-me-down yukata, but you don’t have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:29.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’ve been wanting to get you one as a present for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:34.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be... you used the money in the piggy bank?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:36.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That’s right. Hurry up and try it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.92,0:08:40.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:44.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don’t want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:48.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why? I bought this for you, Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:52.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you spend the money by yourself?{on y’own}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:55.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, “why”? I thought you’d like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:09:00.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, we can always save money again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:04.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, it’s my fault for spending the money without asking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.87,0:09:09.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But since the day’s here, wear your new\Nyukata and let’s go to the fireworks festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.43,0:09:11.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.89,0:09:13.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who cares about the fireworks festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:15.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m not going!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.44,0:09:19.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:31.47,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I saved that money for so long,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:34.24,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,just so we could spend it together at the fireworks festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:38.14,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,The takoyaki stand. The rice cracker stand, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:41.35,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Everything that I was waiting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.82,0:09:45.26,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I really wanted us to eat a big candy apple together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:47.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.54,0:09:58.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m going to return this yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.21,0:10:23.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.71,0:10:26.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to go look for Asu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,0:10:30.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:32.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It’s the same as last time...{HOORAY FOR CONTRIVED CONFLICT}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.02,0:10:45.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Barely made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:49.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu! Asu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:51.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She’s not home yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.90,0:10:54.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she’s okay. Maybe she’s still at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:57.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she’s outside, I hope she found shelter from the rain. {I hope she’s not out in the rain, maybe?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:04.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hate thunder!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.44,0:11:09.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if Asu’s also... {orig: What if... Asu is also...?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.99,0:11:15.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.49,0:11:17.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your sister is coming to get you.{perhaps "alright?" or "okay?" for "ne"}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:24.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The lightning—it hit somewhere nearby.{needs split/retime}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.97,0:11:29.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I think someone told me that lightning is attracted to umbrellas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.77,0:11:42.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:46.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan! Over here! I’m over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.08,0:11:53.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Asu wasn’t afraid of the thunder at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:58.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m so pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:06.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That time, I was so scared of the thunder that when I went to get Asu, I almost gave up halfway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.44,0:12:08.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:15.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe Asu doesn’t even need a sister like me. {alt: Asu might not need a sister like me.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:20.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my, Asu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.77,0:12:21.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What’s wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:24.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You’re completely soaked!{and that yukata you're carrying has unfixable water damage that renders it worthless!}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:27.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if you catch a cold?{I am marking this for editing but will probably forget to fix it}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:30.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ma’am, this yukata—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:33.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, this yukata? You like it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:34.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.95,0:12:37.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has the same design as your sister’s.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:39.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The same?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:43.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why she wouldn’t accept anything else. {alt: Kyo-chan wanted this design no matter what.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:46.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She even went to our warehouse to search for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.08,0:12:49.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She probably spent the whole day looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:52.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The whole day?{alt: All day long?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.47,0:12:59.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She probably felt bad because you’ve never had a yukata to wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.10,0:13:06.63,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,She went to all that trouble just to find a matching yukata for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:08.85,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,For me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:14.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was looking forward to wearing matching yukatas and watching the fireworks together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.45,0:13:15.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It’s okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:18.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It’s just drizzling, so it’ll stop soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:20.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.39,0:13:22.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:26.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The day I forgot my umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.53,0:13:33.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, more lightning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:35.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aww, this is inconvenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.86,0:13:37.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’ll get home late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.64,0:13:41.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:45.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan! Over here! I’m right over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.12,0:13:50.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, you came to pick me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.59,0:13:54.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it looks like the rain has stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:14:00.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn’t even use your umbrella, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:07.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan hates thunder, but she braved it to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:12.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you brought them, let’s use them anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:14.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? But that’s embarrasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.97,0:14:19.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All that and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:21.04,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.11,0:14:25.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I... keep causing trouble for my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:30.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kyou is always looking out for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:31.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told her she was stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.96,0:14:32.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.54,0:14:36.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all she’s done for me, I called her an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.11,0:14:38.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.62,0:14:43.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It’s all right, Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:46.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m not sure what happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.75,0:14:50.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but your sister worked hard searching for this yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:53.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don’t you wear it and show it to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.01,0:14:56.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:09.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:11.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She’s not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:16.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fireworks...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.33,0:15:26.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.02,0:15:31.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.57,0:15:43.13,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:46.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tamaya! Kagiya!
Comment: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:51.93,notes,,0,0,0,,Tamaya and Kagiya were famous rival fireworks manufacturers. At displays, People would root for their favorite, and shouting their names has simply become tradition.{localization: FYUCK YEAR FIERWARKS!!!1}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.94,0:15:51.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every year, Asu and I always watch them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:53.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There’s no point if I’m alone. {alt: Watching them alone is meaningless.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.95,0:15:58.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even so, I expected Asu to be here. {I thought Asu would be here.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.34,0:15:59.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kyou!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:02.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You came just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:05.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your special candy apple is almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:06.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Yaoichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:09.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu was really looking forward to it. {this is terrible. I want to put something like "...so excited for toay" or something}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.79,0:16:11.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said she’d come with her sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:13.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Asu said that? {Asu? Really? <- this may be a better choice, just for variety}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:14.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:18.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She came to see what stands there were, saying she wanted to escort you around the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:19.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.68,0:16:21.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:26.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This memo...
Comment: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:27.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{so are we gonna set this? w}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.72,0:16:32.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu... she scouted out a plan so she could escort me around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:36.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.41,0:16:39.68,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Why did you spend the money by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.41,0:16:42.14,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Who cares about the fireworks festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:43.81,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I’m not going!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.28,0:16:48.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.25,0:16:51.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.45,0:16:57.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, it’s done! The special candy apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:16:59.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Kyou?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.57,0:17:05.06,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Asu wanted to enjoy the festival with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.41,0:17:09.21,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,but I didn’t understand her feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:10.92,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Her feelings.{orig: I threw her feelings away...  <- way too long for the spoken line. I concur.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.20,0:17:16.64,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I promised Mother that I’d take good care of Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.39,0:17:18.62,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I promised her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:25.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:27.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please let me through.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.68,0:17:30.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.62,0:17:34.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to find Onee-chan quickly, before the fireworks are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:36.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:40.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.21,0:17:43.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.17,0:17:46.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.28,0:17:48.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.04,0:18:02.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)}A-su!{should be em dash?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:05.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.59,0:18:09.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.22,0:18:13.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:15.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:18.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:32.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.58,0:18:36.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:39.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you. You wore the yukata.{alt: Thank you for wearing the yukata.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.67,0:18:42.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.49,0:18:44.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, the fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.13,0:18:50.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu, we were able to watch the fireworks{together} again this yea{\fsp-1.5}r.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:53.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:56.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We got to see them again this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.12,0:18:57.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:38.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Won’t you rest a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.75,0:19:42.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu! Why are you here? Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:45.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, I want to work too!{WHY DO WE KEEP DOING GODDAMN SHOWS ABOUT CHILD LABOR}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.42,0:19:50.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don’t have to worry about money.{orig: You can leave the question of money up to me.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.41,0:19:53.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’ll keep working harder and harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.36,0:19:54.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It’s all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.61,0:19:56.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’ll just get another job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:19:57.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:19:59.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.29,0:20:03.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,don’t leave me behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:07.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don’t disappear like Dad did. {daddy would fit better with otou-chan, not otou-san... that said, she is supposed to be 9}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:12.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I called you stupid, but even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:15.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, don’t leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:22.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.94,0:20:26.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan is right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.55,0:20:29.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won’t go anywhere.
Comment: 0,0:20:30.07,0:20:31.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.{Alright}{melody completely omits this, idk if we want to do the same or not}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:34.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It’s all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.22,0:20:36.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.11,0:20:44.06,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Asu, it’s okay. Your sister won’t go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.98,0:20:50.23,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Kyou, you don’t have to worry about not working hard enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:21:00.68,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,The only thing I was able to leave behind for you two was a small promise, but it’s protecting you dearly.{while I agree with that... No idea how to reword to make it not retarded}{idea: The only thing I was able to leave behind for you two was a small promise, but it’s protecting you dearly.}
