Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.31,0:21:11.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sun... {STARING AT THE SUN IS BAD FOR YOUR EYES}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:13.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn’t it pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.68,0:21:14.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.87,0:21:21.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My promise somehow protects the bonds between you two. {ending this with a semicolon just looked wrong}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:24.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will always keep this promise.{orig: I will always... keep this promise.}{what the fuck does "I continue to wish it" even mean. Also, fuck ellipsis overuse.}
