Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.56,0:22:59.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The dark lord of riches!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.09,0:23:02.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? The landlord hasn’t come yet, has he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.02,0:23:03.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what happened.
